- [ ] `skills/sql-agent/scripts/sql-agent.sh` exists and is executable
- [ ] Sources `lib/x-agent-common.sh`
- [ ] `lint` step runs `sqlfluff lint` on all `.sql` files (or scoped)
- [ ] `fix` step defaults OFF, runs `sqlfluff fix` when enabled
