## Implementation Checklist
- [ ] 1. Reconfirm spec requirements and map FRs to existing harness constraints ("'`.ralph/specs/10-sql-agent.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `docs/agents/scenario-tests.md`, `docs/agents/definition-of-done.md`).
