3. What: Implement shared-mode resolution (`resolve_fmt_mode`).
   Why: Required CI-safe behavior for lint/fix mode.
   How: Keep `auto` semantics and force check in CI; preserve explicit mode otherwise.
   Edge Cases: Invalid `FMT_MODE` value.
   Tests: Set `FMT_MODE=bogus`, `CI=true`, `FMT_MODE=auto` scenarios.
